## Verification Plan

### Automated
1. Build passes (`npx next build`)
2. Submit an edit, wait, verify acceptance processing
3. Verify quality tier displays correctly on topic pages

### Manual
1. Change a quality tier as a Level 3+ user — verify it persists
2. Verify Level 2 users cannot advance to Good/Featured tiers
3. Verify flag resolution awards +2 rep to the flagger
4. Verify accepted edits increment `accepted_edits_count`
5. Verify level advancement triggers after sufficient accepted edits
